	<p>Let me introduce the people 
	living in my apartment.</p>
	
	
	<p>
	  Hugo is French. He was born in Toulouse and studied computer science
	  in Paris.
	  Two years ago he met his Japanese girlfriend. 
	  The power of love gave him the dedication to learn 800 kanji in two years.
	  There are special agreements between France and Japan, so he can stay with
	  a "vacance-travaille" visa for one year, working as a waiter.
	  Now I think that I'm learning more French than Japanese here.
	 </p>
	 
	 
